e style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172920TSDPkjlC29OEYnq8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172920czJxMuGP73TboeSp.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172920XqxItzJLKyhDB7aV.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172920cmojNOtkMe8yndFQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172921DcVruXkYfSPeBpbQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172921Or0f3IR9DM7gsHbS.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172921pW5OkVerMnlKq9IY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172921ZdLrG7F0jTMawEUJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172921TuRtMLvbOFpQJGcY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172921piy24rNA0T9IwBWX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925172922pyqWZhMn8x6a2sTL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809251735117yeAX5Sm4YWrjCvl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/spring-2019/paris/jacquemus/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jacquemus 2019 春季成衣系列：</a></strong></p><p>这一季的主题是“La Riviera”，不过也可以叫作“海滩女孩”。Simon Porte Jacquemus 在这个系列中加入了他儿时对于法国南部海滩风光的记忆。“可能有点陈词滥调，但女孩们就是这样。她们会去海边的赌场玩一玩，跳舞，喝鸡尾酒。”</p><p>模特们穿着五颜六色的纯色连体泳衣或不小心就会走光的度假长裙，在意大利驻巴黎大使馆的花园里来回穿梭，手里拿着大得荒谬或小得荒谬的流苏手包，轻松中不失幽默感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181051pADWJs17Ed5k0Mu4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181051ckLFPBAUlsn1Oi3Q.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181052CeOlTdJcPyX2aA4m.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181052mzbE2aZPpDKM5g3I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809251810501K6jXZ7ulMTDwVYa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181053p3S2ivBRAEF81a5X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181053AtVvHGNC2YOnFQxo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181053k8crpUTz2eWRtqBf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181053btEgHxTYe9CGBNyL.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181053f1s5l7DZFAHVxj6I.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181053XI7Lv8JxOobp56eP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809251810541QEBGzZnUptKVHy4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180925181054mwPKJuGAe